So, one of the other fun things

00:35:57.606 --> 00:35:58.916 A:middle
we included is this flag

00:35:58.916 --> 00:35:59.406 A:middle
animation.

00:35:59.696 --> 00:36:00.956 A:middle
It really improves the immersion


00:35:59.696 --> 00:36:00.956 A:middle
It really improves the immersion

